Battera::

She smiled. He still loved her. And that was what mattered most to 
her. "If you are happier with your new form, then I am happy with it. 
No matter what the reason."

She looked as Jynx flew up to them. "Hello there."


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "dachande" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::Dachande/Jynx::
> 
>     He kissed her back, not really caring about explaining as long 
as she still loved him.
>     "Magmatron did that before," He said. "That is actullay how I 
met you. But I changed my look to hide myself from the Alliance, and 
maybe to get back in, and so I would be a better fighter, I mean face 
it, I was a wussy."
>     Jynx flew up right after he heard the word 'wussy' he looked at 
Battera and at Dachande. Then he told Dachande: "Don't be a Wussy, 
there's no reason to be afraid of the Dark."
>
